            <p>Anastasiya works on a one-to-one basis with children from as young as 5 years old.</p>
            <p>In her own unique way Anastasiya emphasises the fun aspect of learning when it comes to giving piano lessons for children so young. This is crucial when working with young pupils, where their attention span is less than that of the older child.</p>
            <p>Anastasiya encourages the involvement of the parent in the initial stage of learning. By sitting in on a few first piano lessons, parents can get a better idea of how to guide and motivate their children's practice at home. When teacher, parent and child are working as a team, the progress and success of the young student is guaranteed.</p>
            <p>The child's interest is maintained through a wide variety of musical styles and repertoire. So whatever their preferences are, whether it be classical, popular, baroque or jazz, all are catered for.</p>
