            <p>Students will be taught how to practice at home in an effective way and will leave each of their piano lessons knowing exactly how to prepare for the next one.</p>
            <p>Music, and in particular playing piano, is much more then a hobby. The disciplines acquired and developed in achieving the students' musical goals can be applied to other aspects of their personal development. It enhances their confidence, memory, problem solving and fine motor skills.</p>
            <p>Over the years, Anastasiya's students, no matter what age they are, have prepared for and completed grade examinations, both the Royal Irish Academy and Associated Board. They have always achieved excellent results and exceeded their own expectations, with all of them getting either Honours or Distinctions.</p>
