            <p>Students, who have prepared for Junior Certificate Music and Leaving Certificate Music in their lessons with Anastasiya, have also achieved excellent results. </p>
            <p>Anastasiya can prepare students for participation in music festivals and competitions, such as Feis Ceoil, if they wish.</p>

            <p>Living in Dublin City provides a wonderful opportunity to explore musical and cultural events. Anastasiya encourages students to attend live performances and concerts, as well as performing for family and friends.</p>
